                        <support>1 papyrus ; 4.5 x 16 cm.</support>
                        <condition>
                           <ab type="conservation">This tall and narrow strip of papyrus is medium-brown in color. It has clearly been cut at all sides, although the edges are more irregular today, probably due to wear and tear. Originally, the strip, which was cut after the text had been written, probably had a shape somewhat similar to a crescent moon. (TC)</ab>
                        </condition>
                     </supportDesc>
                     <layoutDesc>
                        <layout>
