                           <ab type="recto-verso">Source of description: Recto</ab>
                        </layout>
                     </layoutDesc>
                  </objectDesc>
                  <handDesc>
                     <p>The text is written in a rounded hand with lightly cursive elements. After a top margin (1 cm., TC) follows the text which consists of a tall column with 31 lines. At both ends of the lines, no more than 10 letters are missing; the distribution of these letters between the end of one line and the beginning of another must remain an open question.</p>
